data.description:
Welcome to 3517 Morgan River Dr. North located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Ashdale.This residence is a true deepwater gem. Where else can you wake up to a beautiful sunrise over Lucy Creek and Morgan River? This 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home sits on 1.67 acres and has a total square footage of 4164. Some of the most distinctive features of this home include new Heart Pine hardwood floors,a brick fireplace nestled in the living room with built-in shelves and cabinetry, new stainless steel appliances, and shining quartz countertops. One of the most spectacular features includes the Victorian inspired spiral staircase, which adds just the right touch of elegance.From your newly renovated deck, you can enjoy stunning views of the coastline and ever-changing sky. Watch Bald Eagles soar overhead, crabs scuttle along the pluff mud, and Dolphins can be seen almost everyday. How about taking an evening boat cruise to Dataw Marina to eat dinner at Morgan River Grill which is 1 mile away? If you dare to venture, you are also within boating distance of Morgan Island, home to the largest colony of free-range monkeys which are visable from the waterways. What a treat for your family and friends.
Ashdale subdivision is also surrounded by hundreds of acres of conservation land making it safe from future development.
This home is the perfect place to enjoy the best of Lowcountry life. With its stunning views, natural wildlife , and beautiful setting this is the perfect place to call home to relax and reconnect with nature while creating memories that will last a lifetime.
